<paragraph blockId="17.[151,1437,151,1832]" box="[199,624,799,824]" pageId="17" pageNumber="18">
Prosternum: as in 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Saunders Holotype" authorityYear="1876" box="[402,617,800,824]" class="Insecta" family="Buprestidae" genus="Melobasis" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="17" pageNumber="18" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="rubromarginata">
